      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEZA PUNK ROCKER NZ (1) had a tough draw and was held up at his latest appearance at Mildura so prepared to forgive that result. Much better served by this draw and had finished runner-up in his previous two outings here. Can return to the winners' list. LOCHINVAR MAGIC (3) added to a string of top-three results when he led and scored by 4 metres at this circuit and distance last start, the second win from his past four runs. Has the speed to be prominent from this favourable starting position. Contender. LAST TANGO IN HEAVEN NZ (4) is on the radar returning to SA having placed the last time he raced here two back. DON ARTHUR (6) is worth including in exotics after scoring last start by a head at this venue.",
